---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Reflections
description: Reflective writing on faith, memory, meaning, and the shape of life lived in the in-between
---

<div class="endorsement-page shelf-page">

  <p class="essay-back"><a href="/writing/">← Back to The Library</a></p>

  <div class="endorsement-layout shelf-layout">

    <aside class="endorsement-nav shelf-nav">
      <h1>Reflections</h1>

      <p class="endorsement-subtitle shelf-subtitle">
        Reflections that linger with memory, faith, meaning, and the quieter movements of life.
      </p>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/reflections/">Reflections</a>
      </div>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/essays/">Essays</a>
      </div>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/working-papers/">Working Papers</a>
      </div>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/notes/">Notes</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="endorsement-main shelf-main">

      <section class="panel browse-panel">
        <div class="browse-intro">
          <h2>About This Shelf</h2>
          <p>
            This shelf gathers reflective writing that is less concerned with argument than with attention:
            the kind of writing that lingers with experience, memory, faith, and the quiet discovery of meaning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="browse-list">
  {% for item in collections.reflections %}
    <article class="browse-item">
  <a class="browse-item-link" href="{{ item.url }}">
    <h3 class="browse-item-title">{{ item.data.title }}</h3>

    {% if item.data.subtitle %}
      <p class="browse-item-subtitle">{{ item.data.subtitle }}</p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if item.data.description %}
      <p class="browse-item-blurb">{{ item.data.description }}</p>
    {% endif %}
  </a>
</article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
      </section>

    </main>

  </div>
</div>